data.description: Leave your stresses at the end of the driveway & try to keep your jaw off the floor when you see this top quality, gorgeous cabin sitting majestically on just under 23 wooded acres in the heart of Kentucky wilderness. You'll revel in the breathtaking views from the 2 story high living room windows or from the dual level wrap around decks that include an outdoor kitchen area, hot tub & hardwired generator. You'll feel like you escaped from the world but you can still be connected to it with the upgraded high-speed internet service that was just installed & is less than 6 miles from I-75. Fully furnished option available. Buyer to verify all information including square footage, property boundaries, schools, etc.
